<view class='big'>
  <view class="pic">
    <view class="img">
      <swiper class='slid' autoplay="true" interval="2000">
        <block>
          <swiper-item>
            <view class='headView'>
              <image class='icon' src="https://i.loli.net/2021/03/10/AovaeSxTpd19wgB.jpg"></image>
              <view class='icon'></view>
            </view>
            <view class='detail'>
              <view class='userName'>牛油果沙拉</view>
              牛油果沙拉是一道菜品，主料是牛油果、苹果、土司，配料为玉米粒、番茄干。填入沙拉即可。
            </view>
          </swiper-item>
          <swiper-item>
            <view class='headView'>
              <image class='icon' src="https://i.loli.net/2021/03/10/te5NKF8LBrua4RX.jpg"></image>
              <view class='icon'></view>
            </view>
            <view class='detail'>
              <view class='userName'>飞龙汤</view>
              飞龙又名榛鸡是黑龙江省的名菜之一，属于龙江菜系。飞龙汤是将榛鸡脱毛去掉内脏后，用高汤煮熟即可。
            </view>
          </swiper-item>
        </block>

      </swiper>
      <button bindtap="Dishes" class='btn' id="camera">
        <i-icon type="camera_fill" size="28" color="#000" /> 拍照识菜
      </button>
      <view class='xc' bindtap="Dishes" id="album">
        <text>从相册选择></text>
        {{id}}
      </view>
    
    </view>
  </view>


</view>